 are Ready.\\n- Elasticsearch is reachable over HTTPS (port 9200) inside the cluster through a\\n  Service named es-http.\\n- Reads and writes succeed.\",\"numLines\":20,\"startLine\":1,\"totalLines\":20}}}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"thinking_tokens\",\"estimated_tokens\":26,\"estimated_tokens_delta\":26,\"uuid\":\"80826263-27a2-42e2-ab20-96ac240bb87e\",\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"thinking_tokens\",\"estimated_tokens\":43,\"estimated_tokens_delta\":17,\"uuid\":\"04bde4da-ce40-4c16-83c8-7ad932b94ebc\",\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"thinking_tokens\",\"estimated_tokens\":67,\"estimated_tokens_delta\":24,\"uuid\":\"9d83edd3-1af0-4523-b697-92afa77632cd\",\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"thinking_tokens\",\"estimated_tokens\":97,\"estimated_tokens_delta\":30,\"uuid\":\"1990c4e5-e0a5-4512-bb62-abbec69693f1\",\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"thinking_tokens\",\"estimated_tokens\":117,\"estimated_tokens_delta\":20,\"uuid\":\"aa0ae4b9-22cd-4041-ae9c-40e0b4d7255f\",\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"thinking_tokens\",\"estimated_tokens\":138,\"estimated_tokens_delta\":21,\"uuid\":\"0f8602c5-fe5f-4275-9f56-6151ba5b97ec\",\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"thinking_tokens\",\"estimated_tokens\":189,\"estimated_tokens_delta\":51,\"uuid\":\"e6b8821b-d2dd-4636-ae38-b00773b20068\",\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\"}\n{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01RvrsU7rTkrmg24L5WR7kek\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"So the task says secrets should exist (es-http-tls and elastic-password), but they aren't there. However, the cluster IS already deployed and running (3 pods, StatefulSet 3/3, services es-http and es-cluster). But secrets are missing.\\n\\nLooking at the precondition log more carefully - it says 4 pods are running. So the cluster was already deployed as part of a previous run/stage. The current stage_02 prompt is to deploy the cluster from scratch... but it seems like it's already been done.\\n\\nLet me check if the agent.log shows what happened.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":707,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":30843,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":707},\"output_tokens\":33,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"diagnostics\":null,\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\",\"uuid\":\"3b7378db-556d-4068-bbc8-549a40a64167\",\"request_id\":\"req_011Cc5LhecVJtsiHCo8oq8bF\"}\n{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01RvrsU7rTkrmg24L5WR7kek\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_015VqBNckBX3wfsHFHSWqcgg\",\"name\":\"Read\",\"input\":{\"file_path\":\"/Users/leo/Karma/runs/short-examples/elasticsearch-full-lifecycle-20260615_160153/stages/stage_02/agent.log\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":707,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":30843,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":707},\"output_tokens\":33,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"diagnostics\":null,\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\",\"uuid\":\"6aae43a9-112f-4bb1-85