y aren't there. However, the cluster IS already deployed and running (3 pods, StatefulSet 3/3, services es-http and es-cluster). But secrets are missing.\\n\\nLooking at the precondition log more carefully - it says 4 pods are running. So the cluster was already deployed as part of a previous run/stage. The current stage_02 prompt is to deploy the cluster from scratch... but it seems like it's already been done.\\n\\nLet me check if the agent.log shows what happened.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":707,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":30843,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":707},\"output_tokens\":33,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"diagnostics\":null,\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\",\"uuid\":\"3b7378db-556d-4068-bbc8-549a40a64167\",\"request_id\":\"req_011Cc5LhecVJtsiHCo8oq8bF\"}\n{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01RvrsU7rTkrmg24L5WR7kek\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_015VqBNckBX3wfsHFHSWqcgg\",\"name\":\"Read\",\"input\":{\"file_path\":\"/Users/leo/Karma/runs/short-examples/elasticsearch-full-lifecycle-20260615_160153/stages/stage_02/agent.log\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":707,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":30843,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":707},\"output_tokens\":33,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"diagnostics\":null,\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"8d3fdde4-c7f2-4476-8190-13d1882a5e4c\",\"uuid\":\"6aae43a9-112f-4bb1-851